headline: Can UnitedHealth Really Fight Cost Headaches With $3.3B Amedisys Pill?
summary: UNH's $3.3B Amedisys deal will likely clear DOJ hurdles with divestitures, aiming to tap fast-growing home healthcare amid rising cost pressures.
